en.name: Echoes Defense Strikewrap 46 Multi-Caliber sound suppressor (Alpine)
en.description: Engineered by Echoes Defense, the Strikewrap 46 is a high-performance .46 caliber multicaliber suppressor designed for maximum versatility and stealth. Built to dampen the loudest shots with exceptional efficiency, this silencer ensures precision and control in any combat scenario. Available in 12 distinct camouflage variants, the Strikewrap 46 seamlessly adapts to various environments, giving operators the upper hand in tactical engagements. Whether navigating urban warfare or traversing dense terrain, this suppressor’s rugged build and sleek design make it the go-to choice for pros who value silence and adaptability.

en.name: Echoes Defense Nightfall LX .45 ACP sound suppressor
en.description: A pristine .45 ACP suppressor crafted for the USP, its flawless finish gleams under the light, reflecting the craftsmanship of a tool untouched by battle. Silent, sleek, and ready for flawless execution.

en.name: Echoes Defense Nightfall LX .45 ACP sound suppressor (Worn)
en.description: A well-worn .45 ACP suppressor for the USP, bearing scratches and faded engravings that hint at years of silent work in the field. Despite its weathered look, it still delivers deadly quiet precision.

en.name: Haggar Arms Xenon-45 .45 ACP sound suppressor
en.description: The Haggar Arms Xenon-45 is a robust, high-performance suppressor engineered specifically for .45 ACP rounds. Designed for tactical and covert operations, this suppressor significantly reduces both sound and muzzle flash, providing the operator with a quieter shot without sacrificing stopping power. Its durable titanium alloy build ensures longevity and reliable performance, even under sustained fire. The Xenon-45’s compact design and advanced baffle system minimize weight and recoil, making it an excellent choice for close-quarter engagements where stealth is paramount. Whether for professional operators or dedicated enthusiasts, the Xenon-45 delivers unmatched sound suppression and precision.

en.name: Fulson Machine Hex 46 Multi-Caliber sound suppressor
en.description: The Fulson Machine Hex 46 is a cutting-edge multicaliber suppressor engineered by EpicRangeTime Industries, renowned for its reliability and versatility. Capable of handling a wide range of calibers, from 9mm to .45 ACP, this suppressor features a unique hexagonal design that maximizes sound suppression while maintaining balance and precision. Its robust construction ensures durability under heavy use, and the sleek, modern finish makes it a favored choice among elite operators. Whether for tactical missions or range practice, the Hex 46 delivers optimal performance across multiple platforms.

en.name: RSB M-LOK foregrip (FDE)
en.description: A compact and lightweight foregrip designed for precision and control. The RSB M-LOK grip features an ergonomic, low-profile design that enhances weapon handling without adding unnecessary bulk. Machined from durable aluminum, it offers superior strength while maintaining minimal weight. Compatible with all M-LOK mounting systems, this grip is built for operators who demand reliability and performance in high-intensity environments. Perfect for stabilizing rapid fire or maintaining accuracy during prolonged engagements.

en.name: AR-15 Noveske KX3 5.56x45 flash hider (Desert)
en.description:
The Noveske KX3 Flash hider, aka the Burning Pig, is designed to increase reliability in short-barreled members of AR-15 family by increasing backpressure and directing the muzzle blast forward of the shooter. Although originally designed for short-barreled AR-15s, it will work on any barrel length and have since been introduced for a variety of mounts. This particular KX3 may be used on 
5.56mm = 1/2x28 
300BLK, 6.8, & 7.62 = 5/8x24
German rifles = M15x1 
M14x1LH
